connectorAttributes.gradeCode.SQL:
SELECT DISTINCT emp.[Employee_grade_code],
	DisplayName =  
		CASE Employee_grade_code
			WHEN 'AABB' THEN 'Employee Grade 1'
			WHEN 'AABC' THEN 'Employee Grade 2'
			WHEN 'AABD' THEN 'Employee Grade 3'
			ELSE Employee_grade_code
		END, CONCAT('Employee_grade_code:', emp.[Employee_grade_code]) AS IDNid, 'Grade Code' AS description
FROM [dbo].[EMPLOYEE] emp
connectorAttributes.paymentLimit.SQL:
SELECT
    DISTINCT au.[Payment_limit],
    au.[Payment_limit] AS DisplayName,
    'Payment limit' AS description, CONCAT('Payment_limit:', au.[Payment_limit]) AS IDNid
FROM
    [dbo].[APPLICATION_USER] au
WHERE
    au.[Payment_limit] IS NOT NULL
connectorAttributes.travelChargeOutRate.SQL:
SELECT DISTINCT emp.[Travel_charge_out_rate],  emp.[Travel_charge_out_rate] AS DisplayName,  CONCAT('Travel_charge_out_rate:', emp.[Travel_charge_out_rate]) AS IDNid, 'Travel charge out rate' AS description
FROM [dbo].[EMPLOYEE] emp WHERE emp.[Travel_charge_out_rate] IS NOT NULL
connectorAttributes.jobTitle.SQL:
SELECT DISTINCT emp.[Job_title_code],
	DisplayName =  
		CASE Job_title_code
			WHEN 'ACCT' THEN 'Accountant'
			WHEN 'ADJU' THEN 'Adjuster'
			WHEN 'ADMI' THEN 'Administration Assistant'
			WHEN 'AFAA' THEN 'Account Manager'
			WHEN 'AFAH' THEN 'Team Leader'
			WHEN 'APMA' THEN 'Assistant Project Manager'
			WHEN 'ARCO' THEN 'Ariel Coordinator'
			WHEN 'ARTC' THEN 'Ariel Technician'
			WHEN 'ARTM' THEN 'Ariel Team Manager'
			WHEN 'BMGR' THEN 'Branch Manager'
			WHEN 'BSG1' THEN 'Ethics & Compliance Office'
			WHEN 'BUMA' THEN 'Business Unit Manager'
			WHEN 'CASE' THEN 'Rehabilitation Case Manager'
			WHEN 'CFSC' THEN 'CFS Co-ordinator'
			WHEN 'CLAD' THEN 'Corporate/Major Loss Adjuster'
			WHEN 'CLMH' THEN 'Claims Handling Technician'
			WHEN 'CMGR' THEN 'Regional Claims Centre Manager'
			WHEN 'COMP' THEN 'Complaints Manager'
			WHEN 'CONT' THEN 'Contracts Manager'
			WHEN 'CSAT' THEN 'Customer Service Assistant'
			WHEN 'CSSM' THEN 'CSS Regional Manager'
			WHEN 'CSSU' THEN 'CSS UK Operations Manager'
			WHEN 'CSUM' THEN 'CSU Manager'
			WHEN 'CURA' THEN 'Customer Relations Co-ordinator'
			WHEN 'CUSS' THEN 'Customer Support'
			WHEN 'ENGR' THEN 'Engineer'
			WHEN 'HRHB' THEN 'Head of Rehabilitation'
			WHEN 'OPSM' THEN 'Operations Manager'
			WHEN 'PRIM' THEN 'Systems Development'
			WHEN 'PROJ' THEN 'Project Manager'
			WHEN 'ROPS' THEN 'Regional Operations Manager'
			WHEN 'RSCO' THEN 'Rehabilitation Services Coordinator'
			WHEN 'SADM' THEN 'Senior Administrator'
			WHEN 'SURV' THEN 'Surveyor'
			WHEN 'TEAM' THEN 'Team Manager'
			WHEN 'TECD' THEN 'Technical Director'
			WHEN 'TECH' THEN 'Technical Manager'
			WHEN 'UCRM' THEN 'UK Customer Relations Manager'
			WHEN 'VOCC' THEN 'Vocational Consultant'
			ELSE Job_title_code
		END, CONCAT('Job_title_code:', emp.[Job_title_code]) AS IDNid, 'Job title' AS description
FROM [dbo].[EMPLOYEE] emp
connectorAttributes.chargeOutRateEre.SQL:
SELECT DISTINCT emp.[Charge_out_rate_ere_id], emp.[Charge_out_rate_ere_id] AS DisplayName, CONCAT('COREI: ', emp.[Charge_out_rate_ere_id]) AS Description, CONCAT('Charge_out_rate_ere_id:', emp.[Charge_out_rate_ere_id]) AS IDNid
FROM [dbo].[EMPLOYEE] emp
connectorAttributes.profile.SQL:
SELECT [Profile_id], [Profile_name], CONCAT('Profile_id:', [Profile_id]) AS IDNid, 'Profile' AS description
FROM [dbo].[PROFILE]
connectorAttributes.chargeOutRate.SQL:
SELECT DISTINCT emp.[Charge_out_rate],  emp.[Charge_out_rate] AS DisplayName, 'Charge out rate' AS description, CONCAT('Charge_out_rate:', emp.[Charge_out_rate]) AS IDNid
FROM [dbo].[EMPLOYEE] emp
connectorAttributes.SQL:
SELECT 
    FORMAT(emp.[Employee_code], '000000') AS [Employee_code],
    emp.[Last_updated_id] AS [Employee_last_updated_id],
    emp.[Employee_grade_code],
    emp.[Work_tel_no],
    emp.[CTHG_Employee_Code],
    emp.[Last_updated_time] AS [Employee_last_updated_time],
    emp.[Charge_rate_time_period_code],
    emp.[Job_title_code],
    emp.[Work_fax_no],
    emp.[Work_mobile_no],
    emp.[Work_tel_IDC],
    emp.[Work_email_addr],
    emp.[Home_tel_no],
    emp.[Work_fax_IDC],
    emp.[Home_business_tel_no],
    emp.[Home_fax_no],
    emp.[Home_email_addr],
    emp.[Home_tel_IDC],
    emp.[Surname],
    emp.[Forename],
    emp.[Home_business_tel_IDC],
    emp.[Charge_out_rate_ere_id],
    emp.[Leaving_date],
    emp.[Home_fax_IDC],
    emp.[Specialised_knowledge],
    emp.[Required_on_W6_ind],
    emp.[Charge_out_rate],
    emp.[Start_Date],
    emp.[Title_code],
    emp.[Travel_charge_out_rate],
    emp.[Accounting_centre_id],
    emp.[Left_ind],
    emp.[Travel_charge_out_rate_ere_id],
    emp.[Travel_charge_out_rate_time_period_code],
    emp.[Qualifications],
    au.[User_id],
    au.[Profile_id],
    au.[User_status],
    au.[Creation_id],
    au.[Logon_name],
    au.[Last_updated_id] AS [Application_user_last_updated_id],
    au.[User_name],
    au.[Creation_time],
    au.[Last_updated_time] AS [Application_user_last_updated_time],
    au.[Interactive_user],
    CASE
        WHEN au.[Allow_Invoice_Ind] = 'Y' THEN 'Allow_Invoice_Ind'
        ELSE ''
    END AS [Allow_Invoice_Ind],
    CASE
        WHEN au.[Allow_Credit_Note_Ind] = 'Y' THEN 'Allow_Credit_Note_Ind'
        ELSE ''
    END AS [Allow_Credit_Note_Ind],
    CASE
        WHEN au.[Must_View_VAT_Advisory_Ind] = 'Y' THEN 'Must_View_VAT_Advisory_Ind'
        ELSE ''
    END AS [Must_View_VAT_Advisory_Ind],
    au.[Payment_limit],
    CASE
        WHEN User_status = 'DISB' THEN 'true'
        ELSE 'false'
    END AS [IIQDisabled],
    tm.Team_id
FROM
    [dbo].[EMPLOYEE] emp
    LEFT JOIN [dbo].[APPLICATION_USER] au ON au.[Employee_code] = emp.[Employee_code]
    LEFT JOIN [dbo].[TEAM_MEMBER] tm ON tm.[Employee_code] = emp.[Employee_code]
